{"tid":154041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斷咗氣心跳繼續5個鐘 姐承諾照顧妹夫 她才安心走","createTime":"2017-03-13T04:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T05:27:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6a4cba9daad877a5573fe5e42246440dc20ba8","tid":154041,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">【夠晒離奇】斷咗氣心跳繼續5個鐘 姐承諾照顧妹夫 她才安心走<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170313/56417506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170313%2F56417506&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ed5eb548\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170313%2F56417506&h=37be711f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170313/56417506</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n新加坡一位抗癌鬥士直至生命走到盡頭仍不肯低頭，她姐姐表示，妹妹呼吸停頓後心臟還跳動了5小時，家人不忍心，承諾會照顧她丈夫，她的心跳才變弱然後撒手人圜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170312/large/1489306964_d15a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170312%2Flarge%2F1489306964_d15a.jpg&h=3476c553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n56歲旅行社經理楊秀華與牧師丈夫膝下無兒，她10年前患過乳癌，一度戰勝癌症，可是4年前癌症復發，發現肝臟有癌細胞。去年4月她的病情急遽惡化，進出醫院10次。她上月最後一次入院時已經非常虛弱，上周開始更無法說話，延至周四不治。<br />\n<br />\n楊秀華的姐姐感觸表示，妹妹抗癌多年從不言敗，一直奮鬥到最後一刻，「周四早上7點，我們發現她已經沒有呼吸了，可是她的心臟仍正常跳動。醫生一度以為儀器壞了，但換了另一台後結果還是一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n姐姐又說：「家人心知不妙，向她說大家很想她，讓她醒一醒，說到這裡她的心跳會加速。後來她真的不行了，就和她道別，我還告訴她，我會好好照顧她老公，讓她安心走。說到這裡，她的心跳開始變弱，到11點57分停止。」<br />\n<br />\n楊秀華的姐姐形容妹妹是鬥士，「今年初她全身抽搐入院，我們以為她不行了，可是她隔天告訴我，說她一定會出院吃團年飯。她不久後果然出院，除夕還和我們共晉晚餐」。她的丈夫憶起愛妻的種種，更哽咽地道：「她是我們一輩子的驕傲。」"},{"pid":"d7144b115138336f930022797afd244e4d47586c","tid":154041,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf7c77ccdade2195057a476b27d20c9ab63d27b","tid":154041,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"\\l/<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fde836547638ce367d61607c376e9ea9d9cc777","tid":154041,"uid":57139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab4e46ed1aa29654d1fc424a8adb8919e15537d","tid":154041,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"rip"}]}